<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mathusummut/confetti.js/confetti.min.js"></script>
<script>
  (function () {
    const AUTOLOAD = false; //is animation autoloaded on page, if false click on Start button is needed
    const DURATION = 4; //time of animation in seconds only for option AUTOLOAD 
    const START = document.querySelector('[data-sysflow-confetti-start]');
    const STOP = document.querySelector('[data-sysflow-confetti-stop]');
    if(AUTOLOAD) { confetti.start(DURATION*1000) }
    START.addEventListener("click", ()=> {
    	const START_DURATION = +START.dataset.sysflowConfettiStart; 
    	if(START_DURATION) { confetti.start(START_DURATION*1000) }
      else { confetti.start() }
  	})
    STOP.addEventListener("click", ()=>confetti.remove());
   }());
 </script>
